redrawGameMap() - Method in class dynamicStorage.GameInfo
Redraws the map's cells; THIS METHOD SHOULD ONLY BE USED WHEN LOADING A PREVIOUS GAME.
regenerateStringProperties() - Method in class dynamicStorage.GameInfo
Regenerates the string properties used by the game UI; They need to be regenerated because they are not reloaded along with the rest of the GameInfo object when read from the save file because properties aren't serializable.
regenObjectiveEnemies() - Method in class main.GameLogic
Regenerates the enemies in each of the objectives as long as the objective is still hostile;
removeHighlight(MouseEvent) - Method in class main.GameUIController
Redraws the previously hovered over cell with its correct color;
returnToMainMenu(ActionEvent) - Method in class main.GameUIController
